General.Name: Cokal Ltd
General.Description: Cokal Limited engages in the identification and development of coal in Indonesia. Its flagship property is its 60% owned Bumi Barito Mineral project, a metallurgical coal project that covers an area of 14,980 ha located in Kalimantan, Indonesia. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
